      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLACKWOOD RANCH (8) generally breaks well and with clear running can clear the draw. Latest effort finished 4th on March 15 over 330m at this track behind Slick Silas beaten 10 lengths (19.25) in a Maiden. Rates on top and should go close. MADAM HONKY TONK (3) clocked a new course and distance PB last time, finishing a 3 length second behind Paw Iron in 18.99. Strong run and expected to feature again. SLICK STRIKE (1) has been freshened since finishing well back on debut at Wagga over 400m (25.31). Drops down the inside box this time. Can improve sharply here. POKE THE GLASS (2) deserves plenty of thought at her first run at this circuit.",
